      "layout": "The page adheres to a mostly full-bleed layout with content sections but employs a maximum width constraint implicitly for readability within those sections, centered horizontally. The hero section is a full-bleed visual banner, potentially with superimposed text. Section rhythm is primarily driven by color shifts between Canvas Fog, Subtle Ash, and Surface Frost backgrounds, creating distinct visual blocks often separated by thin horizontal lines. Content is frequently arranged in multi-column grids for product listings and alternating text-left/image-right compositions for feature sections. Overall density is compact, prioritizing product visibility in tight grids. Navigation is a sticky top bar with minimal links and a central search input.",
